===Adjective===
'''酸い''' ([[すい]], ''[[sui]]'')

# [[Sour]].

====Etymology====
* Root is '''[[酢]]''' ([[す]], ''[[su]]''), "vinegar".
* Related to the word '''[[すし]]''' (''[[sushi]]''), "vinegared rice".

==== Related terms ====
* '''[[酸っぱい]]''' ([[すっぱい]], ''[[suppai]]''): [[Sour]].  More commonly heard than '''酸い'''.

